<p>Some great listener questions, tips, and especially Cool Stuff Found highlight this week&#39;s episode. John and Dave take you through all of it, ensuring you understand that which is mentioned. Want to know how to measure your Internet bandwidth? Want to sort your Safari Bookmarks? Need to tweak your Menu bar? Anything else you&#39;d like to know? This is the show for you!</p>
